/div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yf3 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">这是没办法知道的。<span class="_ _a"></span>这样用心观察自己的心，<span class="_ _a"></span>最后痛苦的心</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yf4 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">根本找不到。这是比较深的观察方法。 </div><div class="t m0 x1c h4 yf5 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">还有一种观察方法，<span class="_ _a"></span>要认识到我们所遇到的压力，<span class="_ _a"></span>实际</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yf6 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">上是生活的本质，并不是不幸。现在有些年轻人遇到痛苦，</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yf7 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">就想不开，<span class="_ _6"></span>或自杀等等。<span class="_ _8"></span>其实，<span class="_ _6"></span>在人生之路上，<span class="_ _8"></span>这完全不必</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
